  <brief_title>Should Any One Airway Clearance Technique be Recommended for People With Cystic Fibrosis?</brief_title>
  <acronym>ACT</acronym>
  <official_title>A Comparison of Five Airway Clearance Techniques in the Treatment of Adults With Cystic Fibrosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
